<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 9pt">One way to understand such diverse and robust results is to conclude that neurofeedback promotes resilience and flexibility of the central nervous system.<BR>&#1758;&nbsp; Resilient, Efficient – Centered, buoyant, hardy stamina.&nbsp; <BR>&#1758;&nbsp; Flexible, Effective – Agile, adapt, sparkle, creative improvisation.&nbsp; </P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 9pt">Neurofeedback technology has grown in simplicity of use as well as its power.&nbsp; Fitness training for the brain has a broad impact on physical health, mental health, and emotional well-being.&nbsp; <o:p></o:p></P>
<P class=MsoNormal style="MARGIN: 0in 0in 9pt">The central nervous system is central to all that you do. Neurofeedback makes people more effective, more human, more wise.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</P>
